  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A lavish set of exosuit armor, inspired by the traditional designs of Balaron textile merchants. Ornate detailing and plush, padded fabrics elevate the attractiveness and status of the wearer.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>一套豪华的外穿装甲，其设计灵感源自巴拉伦纺织商的传统样式。精美的装饰细节和柔软的填充织物提升了穿戴者的魅力与地位。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>一套豪華的強化套裝裝甲，靈感來自巴拉隆紡織品商人的傳統設計。華美的細節與帶有襯墊的奢華布料，能提升穿戴者的魅力與地位。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
